## ðŸ†˜ If Nothing Works

### Nuclear Option: Complete VSCode Reset

**âš ï¸ WARNING: This will delete ALL VSCode settings, extensions, and data!**

```bash
# Backup your settings first!
cp ~/Library/Application\ Support/Code/User/settings.json ~/vscode-settings-backup.json

# Remove all VSCode data
rm -rf ~/Library/Application\ Support/Code/*
rm -rf ~/.vscode

# Restart VSCode (it will be like a fresh install)

# Reinstall KOMPLETE-KONTROL
code --install-extension /Users/imorgado/Projects/Roo-Code/bin/komplete-kontrol-3.38.1.vsix --force

# Restore your settings
cp ~/vscode-settings-backup.json ~/Library/Application\ Support/Code/User/settings.json
```

