## âœ… Success Checklist

After following these steps, you should have:

- [ ] All old extensions uninstalled (nothing shows when searching "roo" or "cline")
- [ ] Cache cleared
- [ ] New VSIX installed
- [ ] VSCode fully restarted (quit and reopened, not just reloaded)
- [ ] "KOMPLETE-KONTROL" appears in Activity Bar
- [ ] Cmd+Shift+P shows KOMPLETE-KONTROL commands
- [ ] Extension panel opens when clicking the icon

